synopsis: Bondi James, otherwise known as Agent BJ, is young, hung and full of verve. He lives for one thing: to catch spies and surfing. He enlists the help of a talking chimp to engage in a luscious journey to Wolfhound Island to stop the devious and evil Alpha Dog's plans for universal domination.
tagline: A secret agent who doesn't work for peanuts

titre: Sin Tu Permiso: Nosotras en la escena Hardcore y Punk Estatal
realisateur: ['Esther Galván Rubio', 'Carolina Herrero Schell', 'Marina López Baena', 'Ana Martínez Martín']
